title: Penn Thai
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Thai, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Thai food menu. Marks the vegetarian dishes, which can be made vegan upon request. Say no egg or fish sauce. Dairy is in desserts not mains. Staff understand what vegan is. Atmosphere bright and simple with plastic covered tables and photos of dishes displayed in window. Restaurant was under a previous ownership as She's Thai, which was known for being vegan-friendly, and while menu has changed, vegan choices still available.
